						"title": "Guide: The SASE buyer's guide for Cloudflare customers",
						"subtitle": "Accelerate your journey to SASE: A Buyer's guide for existing customers",
						"copy": "Many organizations start with Cloudflare to secure external-facing apps. This guide helps you take the next step—protecting users, data, and internal apps with a Secure Access Service Edge (SASE) or Security Service Edge (SSE) architecture.\n\nDesigned for existing customers, the guide helps CISOs, CIOs, and heads of networking:\n- Pinpoint high-impact, near-term SASE use cases\n- Align it and security priorities\n- Assess vendors and build a practical, future-ready roadmap\n\nStart your SASE journey with clarity—leveraging the foundation you've already built with us.\n\n![Ebook SASE Buyers - Thumbnail](//cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/slt3lc6tev37/6pvO0d7304FuU93Or90vvK/3d826b1eaee135bd6603dcefac80b19d/ebook_Thumbnail__1_.png)",
